    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem of a car. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no dents, and the interior is just spotless. It drives like a total dream and has been pampered since day one. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
